45
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:44,800
Pay attention to the waveforms and the telemetry signals.

46
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:52,000
The wheel is operating normally.

47
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,600
The waveform from the Hall effect sensor is not showing spikes.

48
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:58,300
