Fine.

266
00:22:05,960 --> 00:22:08,940
You don't carry me anymore, and you haven't been playing.

267
00:22:11,279 --> 00:22:14,119
Xia Qing came to Shanghai and asked me out for a drink.

268
00:22:16,039 --> 00:22:18,579
You know what that means and what she wants.

269
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:22,039
It's the weekend tomorrow.

270
00:22:22,039 --> 00:22:25,539
- If you have the time... 
 - I'm busy. I don't see the point either.

271
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,040
Fine.

272
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,800
Don't eat too much.

273
00:22:56,599 --> 00:22:58,119
 Yu Tu is quite busy. 

274
00:22:58,119 --> 00:23:01,599
 You know about them aerospace people. The team is always working overtime. 

275
00:23:01,599 --> 00:23:03,480
 He is too busy to hang out. 

276
00:23:03,480 --> 00:23:07,420
 He lives in the suburbs. A round trip takes three hours. 

277
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,380
 Send me the address of his workplace. 

278
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:19,700
She is very persistent.

279
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:38,200
   
 Zhai Liang told me you were working overtime. 

280
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:40,040
 Do you have time to grab a tea later? 

281
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:58,200
   

282
00:23:58,200 --> 00:24:01,580
That's all for our plans for the field test.

283
00:24:01,580 --> 00:24:03,700
Are there any questions?

284
00:24:06,759 --> 00:24:08,779
Very well. Dismissed.

285
00:24:08,779 --> 00:24:12,159
It's the weekend, go home and rest well.

286
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:28,640
 I'm waiting at the coffee shop next to your workplace. 

287
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:31,279
We got off work at 8 p.m. We can bear hardship,

288
00:24:31,279 --> 00:24:33,200
we have no fear of overtime work.

289
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:35,580
Let's go. Let's have hot pot together.

290
00:24:36,279 --> 00:24:38,359
Go on without me. I have things to do.

291
00:24:39,079 --> 00:24:40,679
See you.

292
00:24:57,519 --> 00:24:59,680
Miss, do you need more water?

293
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,839
Never mind.

294
00:25:00,839 --> 00:25:02,039
Very well.

295
00:25:07,360 --> 00:25:08,860
 Yu Tu. 

296
00:25:14,860 --> 00:25:17,339
 Have you decided on what I told you earlier? 

297
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:21,299
 If you have no plans for our future, 

298
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:24,100
 then we might as well break up. 

299
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:28,780
 Fine. I have no problems with it. 

300
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:43,399
 If I could win his heart back then, I can win it again. 

301
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:48,579
 They were just playing games. What's the big deal? 

302
00:25:48,579 --> 00:25:50,960
 Don't be so obsessed with him. 

303
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:55,019
 Tons of people are wooing you, but you want to get him back? 

304
00:25:55,019 --> 00:25:57,759
 Yu Tu is still working in the institute. 

305
00:25:57,759 --> 00:26:01,399
 He's still getting that meager salary. That doesn't bother you now? 

306
00:26:02,359 --> 00:26:04,560
 I don't care about his salary now. 

307
00:26:05,799 --> 00:26:08,350
 He has a Ph.D., and works in the institute. 

308
00:26:08,350 --> 00:26:10,730
 At least his social status is high. 

309
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,980
 Not to mention... 

310
00:26:14,499 --> 00:26:16,240
 I can't move on. 

311
00:26:17,380 --> 00:26:19,260
 I just can't move on. 

312
00:26:44,799 --> 00:26:47,400
Your workplace is quite a distance from downtown.

313
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:49,519
Zhai Liang told me your phone often has no reception.

314
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:51,240
He was right.

315
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:55,039
Is it for confidentiality? Can't you have phones inside the lab?

316
00:26:55,039 --> 00:26:56,779
Why did you want to see me?

317
00:26:58,160 --> 00:27:00,160
I've been waiting for over two hours.

318
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:02,919
Do you expect me to leave after just a few words?

319
00:27:03,559 --> 00:27:06,079
Did you have dinner? Should we order some food?

320
00:27:06,079 --> 00:27:07,579
I've had dinner.

321
00:27:08,839 --> 00:27:11,359
Sir, may I take your order?

322
00:27:11,359 --> 00:27:13,480
Okay. No, thanks.

323
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,959
Sure.

324
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:23,140
Zhai Liang and I sat here for a while.

325
00:27:23,140 --> 00:27:25,359
I heard you started working at the institute again.

326
00:27:25,359 --> 00:27:26,659
Yes.

327
00:27:28,359 --> 00:27:30,380
He is worried about you.

328
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:33,659
He knew you were stressed. But he didn't want to pry.

329
00:27:33,659 --> 00:27:36,259
Is there some issue with the investment bank?

330
00:27:37,279 --> 00:27:39,079
No.

331
00:27:39,079 --> 00:27:41,000
I'm more suited for the institute.

332
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:47,399
A person's mindset can change.

333
00:27:48,079 --> 00:27:53,019
I think you're a man of focus. The job at the institute suits you.

334
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:55,559
We were talking about it last night at the gathering.

335
00:27:55,559 --> 00:28:01,639
I even joked that your brilliant mind should best be used for contributions to science.

336
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:15,340
I even argued with you over this matter in the past.

337
00:28:15,340 --> 00:28:17,659
I was too young and silly.

338
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:21,399
I thought I was right.

339
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:45,040
By the way, how did you end up playing games with Qiao Jingjing?

340
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,799
We were discussing it during the gathering last night.

341
00:28:48,799 --> 00:28:53,639
Some blamed us for not telling people we studied in the same high school as her.

342
00:28:53,639 --> 00:28:55,680
It's hard to tell people about it.

343
00:28:55,680 --> 00:29:00,040
We barely know her. Did you two also drink together?

344
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:05,959
I pondered on it, but that seemed unlikely.

345
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:08,579
So as soon as they left,

346
00:29:09,759 --> 00:29:12,119
I came by to confirm it with you.

347
00:29:16,759 --> 00:29:18,600
So it really was her.

348
00:29:21,480 --> 00:29:23,600
We were high school classmates.

349
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:25,660
It's normal that we stayed in touch.

350
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,340
Indeed.

351
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:31,960
But she was never in the class group chat.

352
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:35,040
I thought she didn't like hanging out with her old classmates.

353
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:41,499
Perhaps... she is the most successful from our class.

354
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:47,600
We, on the other hand, haven't achieved anything.

355
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:50,900
The moment we step into society, grades won't do us any merit.

356
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,919
It comes down to our EQ.

357
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:56,060
She graduated from a key university.

358
00:29:56,759 --> 00:29:58,459
Is that so?

359
00:30:00,039 --> 00:30:02,759
I didn't pay much attention to her back then.

360
00:30:03,519 --> 00:30:05,900
But I do find her achievement impressive.

361
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:08,680
Entertainment is a complicated industry.

362
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:11,079
There are bad people in the business.

363
00:30:11,079 --> 00:30:14,499
She has managed to find success and become famous,

364
00:30:14,499 --> 00:30:16,760
she must have sacrificed a lot.

365
00:30:23,260 --> 00:30:24,760
Xia Qing.

366
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:30,640
I think... I owe you an apology.

367
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:40,039
I agreed to date you back then because you were capable and independent.

368
00:30:40,039 --> 00:30:42,399
But it never occurred to me that I should return your love.

369
00:30:43,319 --> 00:30:47,819
It turned out that I was not an ideal choice for you.

370
00:30:49,060 --> 00:30:53,120
But you were always smart. You put an end to our relationship in time.

371
00:31:14,759 --> 00:31:16,919
Is this supposed to be your generosity?

372
00:31:23,717 --> 00:31:26,317
It's been too long since we last talked.

373
00:31:26,317 --> 00:31:28,120
This is uncalled for.

374
00:31:34,519 --> 00:31:36,719
I see now why you chose to return to the institute.

375
00:31:37,419 --> 00:31:40,240
After all, worldly possessions no longer concern you.

376
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:45,420
Hold on to your precious chance.

377
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:28,279
♪  Happy Birthday to you!  ♪

378
00:32:28,279 --> 00:32:30,420
 Jingjing, blow out the candles! 

379
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:37,700
 Happy Birthday! 

380
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,199
I...

381
00:33:41,119 --> 00:33:44,259
I sent Xia Qing the address of your workplace. I hope you're not offended.

382
00:33:44,259 --> 00:33:45,920
It's all right.

383
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:50,619
It was mostly because she seemed a little persistent this time around.

384
00:33:51,599 --> 00:33:53,879
I doubt she would contact me again.

385
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,900
A heart of stone.

386
00:33:58,039 --> 00:33:59,959
I forgot to remind you.

387
00:33:59,959 --> 00:34:02,339
Did you tell them Jingjing and I...

388
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,680
were playing games together?

389
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:08,280
Of course not. You told me not to tell anyone.

390
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,880
I just pretended I didn't know her.

391
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:12,620
I won't tell others how bad she was at the game.

392
00:34:16,719 --> 00:34:21,300
So... in your heart, she's...

393
00:34:30,079 --> 00:34:32,559
Cotton is pretty adorable.

394
00:34:32,559 --> 00:34:34,760
She is energetic and cute. She's like a little girl.

395
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:40,400
You two studied in the same high school, but the distance... is a little too far.

396
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:44,419
I'm not saying she's beyond your league.

397
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:48,700
I think...

398
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:53,639
We played games with her for almost two months,

399
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:57,040
and she disappeared without a word.

400
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:02,720
A superstar should always keep her distance from us.

401
00:35:08,239 --> 00:35:09,760
Did you

402
00:35:11,516 --> 00:35:13,376
see her go online again?

403
00:35:13,376 --> 00:35:15,920
I checked the game history.

404
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,580
It's stopped on the day of your match.

405
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:21,410
The last two matches were impressive.

406
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:30,699
She gave me two tickets and invited both of us.

407
00:35:31,639 --> 00:35:33,139
But I didn't tell you.

408
00:35:34,260 --> 00:35:35,560
What?

409
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:38,259
Did she give me a ticket, too?

410
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,860
It's on the bookshelves.

411
00:35:54,740 --> 00:35:56,321
Zhai Liang.

